    <string-array name="dice_rules">
        <item>Each player spins the dual wheel — outer ring is body, inner ring is action (8 segments each).</item>
        <item>Outer ring is body zones (8 segments). Inner ring is actions (8 segments). Match the on-screen words to your comfort.</item>
        <item>Actions include Kiss, Lick, Massage, playful bite, trace slowly, soft blow, hold, and You Choose — body zones include neck through Partner Chooses.</item>
        <item>On your turn, spin and perform the action on the body part you landed on.</item>
        <item>Take turns spinning. Use the timer if you turned it on in session setup.</item>
        <item>Double spin: if both rings land on the same number, you choose any body part and any action (by agreement).</item>
        <item>Keep a consent signal — tap a hand to stop, smile or nod to continue.</item>
        <item>The round ends after five turns each (or when you stop).</item>
        <item>Always prioritize fun, consent, and teasing. Stop or skip anything that doesn\'t feel right.</item>
    </string-array>
